<title>TURKEY: Koc Hldg secures $100 mln loan.</title>
<headline>Koc Hldg secures $100 mln loan.</headline>
<dateline>ISTANBUL 1996-09-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Turkey's leading industrial conglomerate Koc Holding A.S. said it secured a $100 million, three-year loan from international markets through a consortium of 10 banks.</p>
<p>In a statement sent to the Istanbul Stock Exchange, the Holding said the loan carried an interest rate of LIBOR plus 120 basis points, with interest repayments due every six-months.</p>
<p>The loan will be used by companies within the Koc group. -- Istanbul newsroom +90-212-2750875.</p>
